    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_06_02-hrk018.m4a",
      "text": "すぐ喧嘩になるから、スリクスさんは出来るだけ\n喋らないようにしようってことになって……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "They start fighting immediately‚\nso we decided it's best if IIIX doesn't talk much…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 161.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_06_02-hrk019.m4a",
      "text": "おかげでみんな、温泉に入ってる間\nずっと黙り込んでたんだから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Because of that‚ everyone was silent the whole time\nwhen we were in the hot spring.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 166.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenlobby-00-noon",
      "startTime": 169.7
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_06_02-hrk020.m4a",
      "text": "今夜はずっとあの調子だと思うと気が重いわね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thinking about tonight being the same way is kind of depressing.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 169.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenlobby-00-noon",
      "startTime": 174
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_06_02-hrk021.m4a",
      "text": "はぁ……これがプライベートの旅行だったら\n気楽に温泉を楽しめたのに",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sigh… If this were a private trip‚\nI could have enjoyed the hot spring more casually.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 177.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_06_02-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "遙子さんはプライベートで\n温泉旅行に行ったりするんですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Do you go on hot spring trips\nin your private time‚ Haruko-san?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 182.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenlobby-00-noon",
      "startTime": 184.8666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_06_02-hrk022.m4a",
      "text": "全く行ってないかな……\nでも、大学の友達は彼氏と温泉旅行をしたらしくて……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I guess I haven't really gone on a trip like that…\nBut my college friends went on hot spring trips with their boyfriends…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 187.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenlobby-00-noon",
      "startTime": 193.1
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
