      "text": "羨ましい訳じゃないけど、みんな青春してるんだな～\nって思ったら、いろいろ考えちゃって……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm not jealous‚ but everyone is really enjoying their youth…\nWhen I think about it‚ I start pondering all sorts of things…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 197.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
