      "text": "彼氏と温泉旅行ですか\n遙子さんもそういうのに憧れがあるんですね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "A hot spring trip with a boyfriend?\nHaruko-san‚ do you also long for something like that?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 204.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
