      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_06_02-hrk024.m4a",
      "text": "そりゃあ、全く憧れがないかというと……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well‚ I can't say I have no desire for it at all…",
